<headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued July 03 at 6:55PM MDT until July 03 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 423 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 8 PM MDT THIS
EVENING FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS
IN MONTANA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 5 COUNTIES
IN CENTRAL MONTANA
FERGUS                JUDITH BASIN          MEAGHER
IN SOUTHWEST MONTANA
BROADWATER            JEFFERSON
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BOULDER, BOULDER HILL,
DEEP CREEK PASS, ELK PARK PASS, GRASS RANGE, HOBSON,
HOMESTAKE PASS, LEWISTOWN, LEWISTOWN DIVIDE, MARTINSDALE,
MONTANA CITY, RAYNESFORD, STANFORD, TOSTON, TOWNSEND,
WHITE SULPHUR SPRINGS, WHITEHALL, WINIFRED, AND WINSTON.</description>
